Third-Party Notices (Draft)
Updated: 2025-12-13

This project is licensed under the MIT License (see `LICENSE`).
This file is a draft and is not legal advice.

Runtime dependencies not distributed with this repository:

- Python (PSF License / PSF-2.0) — required to run the backend from source.
- Pillow (PIL / HPND) — required for image thumbnail generation (`pip install -r backend/requirements.txt`).
- FFmpeg (LGPL-2.1-or-later or GPL-2.0-or-later, depending on build) — optional external tool
  for video frame extraction and thumbnails. Default integration is via external CLI and
  users install/provide `ffmpeg.exe` and `ffprobe.exe` themselves.

Planned/optional dependencies (not currently included in this repository):

- Video.js — Apache License 2.0 — enhanced video playback UI.

If a release bundles any third-party binaries or source code, the corresponding license texts
and required notices should be included alongside this file and documented under
`doc/licenses/`.
